scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 2-189 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including all 'Parts' (1-7) and their respective provisions. The text before line 2 is introductory, and lines after 189 are signatures and authorizations. The Schedule is the negotiated supplement to the standard ISDA Master Agreement, and this span excludes standard pre-print, CSA annexes, and other extraneous material.
